resources.string: What is your favorite Cunda face?

"I am Cunda, you may or may not know this about me but I really like to eat fish.\n Also I am the best dog in the world. I care about my family and just can\'t stand when my siblings fight, or when they\'re sad.\n And just so you\'ll know mom you\'re my favorite, and I know you love me even though you don\'t let me in bed with you."
